737
00:47:02,830 --> 00:47:03,870
Ya.

738
00:47:05,740 --> 00:47:07,370
Entahlah.

739
00:47:08,269 --> 00:47:09,640
Baiklah.

740
00:47:09,709 --> 00:47:13,039
Menurut kalian siapa yang paling pertama berciuman?

741
00:47:13,109 --> 00:47:14,609
