745
00:47:24,160 --> 00:47:26,019
Satu, dua, tiga, empat, lima.

746
00:47:26,089 --> 00:47:27,129
Angkat tangan yang memilih Mi Rae.

747
00:47:27,189 --> 00:47:28,589
Satu, dua, tiga, empat, lima.

748
00:47:28,660 --> 00:47:30,399
