749
00:47:30,459 --> 00:47:32,030
- Tentu saja.
- Tentu saja.

750
00:47:32,100 --> 00:47:35,629
Minum berpasangan.

751
00:47:35,700 --> 00:47:37,769
- Minum berpasangan.
