756
00:47:51,019 --> 00:47:52,019
Berikan itu.

757
00:47:52,220 --> 00:47:53,249
Apa?

758
00:47:56,450 --> 00:47:57,490
Terima kasih.

759
00:47:57,560 --> 00:48:00,019
Perlukah dia menyatakan keinginan atas bantuannya?

