773
00:48:40,899 --> 00:48:44,100
- Minumlah.
- Minumlah.

774
00:48:45,769 --> 00:48:47,069
Astaga.

775
00:48:47,269 --> 00:48:49,370
Dia sudah gila?

776
00:48:50,780 --> 00:48:52,010
