784
00:49:21,810 --> 00:49:22,939
Ini gila.

785
00:49:23,209 --> 00:49:25,539
- Astaga.
- Terlalu norak.

786
00:49:28,010 --> 00:49:29,010
Aku menyukaimu.

787
00:49:29,850 --> 00:49:31,050
Ayo pacaran, Soo A.

788
00:49:36,149 --> 00:49:37,160
Jantan sekali.

789
00:49:40,330 --> 00:49:41,359
Hebat.

790
00:49:45,660 --> 00:49:46,660
