797
00:50:08,249 --> 00:50:10,289
Kita akan tetap seperti itu,

798
00:50:11,319 --> 00:50:12,419
ya?

799
00:50:14,359 --> 00:50:17,100
Tentu saja, kita semua teman.

800
00:50:18,600 --> 00:50:19,600
Benar?

801
00:50:20,030 --> 00:50:21,169
Ayo cari udara segar.

802
00:50:21,229 --> 00:50:25,069
Astaga, si Bodoh itu tidak tahu siapa yang dia sukai.

803
00:50:25,140 --> 00:50:27,410
- Semoga kalian makin akrab.
- Bertemanlah.

804
00:50:28,039 --> 00:50:29,069
Astaga.

805
00:50:36,649 --> 00:50:38,220
Kalian bersenang-senang?

806
00:50:38,580 --> 00:50:40,789
- Hai.
- Hai.

807
00:50:52,959 --> 00:50:54,930
