817
00:51:19,720 --> 00:51:21,589
Bagaimana jika kita makan ayam dan bir seusai kuliah?

818
00:51:21,660 --> 00:51:22,689
Bagaimana?

819
00:51:23,700 --> 00:51:26,330
Jika Soo A mau,

820
00:51:26,930 --> 00:51:28,169
