- Kamu ini kenapa, Kyung Seok?

862
00:54:09,530 --> 00:54:11,359
- Minta maaf sekarang juga.
- Minta maaflah.

863
00:54:12,030 --> 00:54:13,330
Kyung Seok!

864
00:54:18,999 --> 00:54:19,999
Maafkan aku.

865
00:54:21,609 --> 00:54:23,140
