868
00:54:28,149 --> 00:54:30,319
Mungkin dia salah paham.

869
00:54:35,189 --> 00:54:36,249
Soo A.

870
00:54:41,760 --> 00:54:43,899
Kamu ini kenapa?

871
00:54:44,729 --> 00:54:47,330
