00:57:47,350 --> 00:57:48,879
Bukan begitu.

925
00:57:50,979 --> 00:57:52,749
Aku berteman dengan Mi Rae.

926
00:57:53,379 --> 00:57:54,390
Apa?

927
00:57:54,450 --> 00:57:57,959
